<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Server Error</title>
<style>
  :root {
    --primary-color: #3f51b5;
    --hover-color: #303f9f;
    --error-color: #f44336;
    --text-color: #455a64;
    --light-bg: #f5f7fa;
  }

  body {
    font-family: 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
    text-align: center;
    background-color: var(--light-bg);
    color: var(--text-color);
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    min-height: 100vh;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .error-container {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 40px 20px;
    background-color: white;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }

  h1 {
    color: var(--error-color);
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .ascii-art {
    font-family: monospace;
    color: var(--text-color);
    margin: 30px 0;
    font-size: 1.1em;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .message {
    font-size: 1.3em;
    margin: 25px 0;
    padding: 15px;
    background-color: #fff8e1;
    border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
    text-align: left;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  .message-label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.85em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    color: #7e57c2;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .funny-text {
    margin: 25px 0;
    font-size: 1.1em;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .home-button {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 30px;
    padding: 12px 24px;
    font-size: 1em;
    color: white;
    background-color: var(--primary-color);
    border: none;
    border-radius: 4px;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
  }

  .home-button:hover {
    background-color: var(--hover-color);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .error-container {
      margin: 15px;
    }
    
    h1 {
      font-size: 1.7rem;
    }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="error-container">
  <h1>Houston, We Have a Problem</h1>
  <div class="ascii-art">
    <pre>
     .-""""""-.
    .' _      '.
   /  (o)  (o)  \
  :   ___/\___   :
  |  (         )  |
  : '.\_____./.' :
   \     '     /
    '._     _.'
      '-...-'  
    </pre>
  </div>
  <div class="message">
    <span class="message-label">Server says:</span>
    "{{message}}"
  </div>
  <p class="funny-text">Our tech team is currently working on it. Perhaps this is a good time for that coffee break you've been postponing? â˜•</p>
  <p class="funny-text">We promise we're typing furiously to get things back up and running!</p>
  <a href="/" class="home-button">Return to Safety</a>
</div>
</body>
</html>